                  <p class="bh">
                    <span class="bf">This announcement contains inside information as stipulated under the<location value="LC/gb" idsrc="xmltag.org">UK</location>version of the Market Abuse Regulation No 596/2014 which is part of English Law by virtue of the European (Withdrawal) Act 2018, as amended. On publication of this announcement via a Regulatory Information Service, this information is considered to be in the public domain.</span>
